Author: janm
Content: What is the problem you have with SMP support in FreeBSD?

Author: janm
Content: 64 bit support on FreeBSD is pretty good; the only real issue is being able to compile for 32 bit targets on a 64 bit host out of the box.  The ULE scheduler improves SMP support considerably.
